  fix ROOT misuse

  12 Jun 2006; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  fix changelog

*twoftpd-1.21 (14 May 2006)

  14 May 2006; Thilo Bangert <bangert@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
